                = to_ten_thousands(@candidate["in"]["in_civil"])
            .graphic-body
              .gpb-03 style="width: #{get_percentage(@candidate["in"]["in_civil"], @candidate["in_total"])}"
          .gp-bar
            p
              | 政黨捐贈：
